• **1124-1126**: [John Capellanus](/John_Capellanus)
• **1126-1143**: [Herbert of Selkirk](/Herbert_of_Selkirk)
• **bef.1143-1145**: [Edward](/Edward_of_Aberdeen), [Bishop of Aberdeen](/Bishop_of_Aberdeen)
• **c.1147–c.1150**: [William Cumin](/William_Cumin)
• **bef.1150-1153**: Walter, possibly [Walter fitz Alan](/Walter_fitz_Alan)

